{"tid":2287374,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消息指油麻地起火單位為尼泊爾餐廳　事發時正開生日會","createTime":"2020-11-15T16:41:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T07:15:15.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"13c5c06a7a3659e09c515c09df70747cb0a57856","tid":2287374,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:41:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560137-20201116.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560137-20201116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3hR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=0f155b5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1560137-20201116.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=9191de96\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1560137-20201116.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n油麻地廣東道560號晚上有唐樓起火，造成17人死傷，當中4男3女死亡，7人危殆，1人嚴重。消防正在調查起火原因。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，起火樓宇樓高4層，屬商住唐樓，起火單位為1樓的尼泊爾餐廳，其中一個傷者的兒子當時正開生日派對。<br />\n<br />\n據初步了解，傷者表示在起火單位門前見到有燃燒的蠟燭放在地上，並可能燒著旁邊的隔音板而引起大火。傷者表示有9名親戚，當時一同在餐廳內開生日會。"},{"pid":"1bbb3e2818ee4828fe93e67cd247087cd7ca4011","tid":2287374,"uid":199670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:42:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423e1c868150b284f218a87c7d26e18b85ac89a2","tid":2287374,"uid":72173,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-15T16:43:41.000Z","msg":"限聚令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1ad833ceb00652f2ac68c4bff1866fc747f5e81","tid":2287374,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit